               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>HOMAN, <rs id="t18070701-69-verdict428" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070701-69-verdict428" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
